data.description: Beautiful home with great back deck overlooking large wooded retreat! Inviting foyer with study/living room, formal dining room with Bayed window. Large open family room with built in book cases, ceiling fan and lots of windows. Updated kitchen with stainless appliances, granite countertops, island and hardwood floors. Keeping room off family and breakfast area. Keeping room with bar area and wood burning stove. Relaxing covered patio overlooking private wooded oasis with walking trails, gazebo, electricity and irrigation system. Updated powder room with shiplap, deep two car garage with workbench. Master bedroom with large master bath with granite counter tops, three additional bedrooms, and hall bath. One of the bedrooms is oversized and perfect for a teenage suite. Unfinished basement with HVAC. Great place to call home with no HOA. Great location. Close to schools, shopping and downtown Woodstock.
